Creating a workspace&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This usually requires specifying a name and a path. I prefer a convention where my secondary workspaces are siblings of my default workspace directory, named with a suffix. Assuming your &lt;strong&gt;default&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; workspace is at &lt;code&gt;~&#x2F;project&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, I prefer the new workspace named &lt;code&gt;foo&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; to be at &lt;code&gt;~&#x2F;project.foo&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color-scheme: light dark; color: light-dark(#383A42, #ABB2BF); background-color: light-dark(#FAFAFA, #282C34);&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#A0A1A7, #7F848E);font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#A0A1A7, #7F848E);font-style: italic;&quot;&gt; Get the path of the default workspace&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#E45649, #E06C75);&quot;&gt;repo_dir&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#383A42, #56B6C2);&quot;&gt;=&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#4078F2, #61AFEF);&quot;&gt;jj&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; workspace&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; root&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#986801, #D19A66);&quot;&gt; -&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#986801, #D19A66);&quot;&gt;-name&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; default&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#A0A1A7, #7F848E);font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#A0A1A7, #7F848E);font-style: italic;&quot;&gt; Create the new workspace at the same level with a suffix&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#4078F2, #61AFEF);&quot;&gt;jj&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; workspace&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; add&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#986801, #D19A66);&quot;&gt; -&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#986801, #D19A66);&quot;&gt;-name&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; foo&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#E45649, #E06C75);&quot;&gt; $&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#E45649, #E06C75);&quot;&gt;repo_dir&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;.foo&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To simplify this, you can define a Jujutsu alias in &lt;code&gt;~&#x2F;.config&#x2F;jj&#x2F;config.toml&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color-scheme: light dark; color: light-dark(#383A42, #ABB2BF); background-color: light-dark(#FAFAFA, #282C34);&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;toml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#4078F2, #61AFEF);&quot;&gt;aliases&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#E45649, #E06C75);&quot;&gt;wa&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; =&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; [&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;  &amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;util&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;exec&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;--&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;bash&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;-c&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;  &amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;jj workspace add --name $0 $(jj workspace root --name default).$0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then, you can simply run:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color-scheme: light dark; color: light-dark(#383A42, #ABB2BF); background-color: light-dark(#FAFAFA, #282C34);&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#4078F2, #61AFEF);&quot;&gt;jj&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; wa&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(#50A14F, #98C379);&quot;&gt; foo&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h4 id=&quot;switching-between-workspaces&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;permalink&quot; href=&quot;#switching-between-workspaces&quot;&gt;
