Conclusion&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using a simple naming convention coupled with these aliases makes workspaces feel like a natural part of my workflow, not a chore. It lets me switch tasks instantly, helping me stay focused while keeping my work organized.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#x27;ve been using this approach with my &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gist.github.com&#x2F;pksunkara&#x2F;622bc04242d402c4e43c7328234fd01c&quot;&gt;jj aliases&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; for a while, and it works great!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
